<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no"  />
    <title>邀请好友</title>
    <link href="css/beauty-point.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <body class="bg-f0f0f0">
        <section class="invite-page">
            <div class="pager-top-item"></div>
            <section class="con-wrap">
                <div class="invite-num-item">
                    <div class="listItem">您的邀请码</div>
                    <div class="num">46849724</div>
                </div>
                <div class="btn-wrap">
                    <a href="#" class="btn share-btn notclick-btn">
                        <i class="icon share-icon"></i>
                        <span class="txt">邀请好友，获得100积分</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="btn text-btn notclick-btn">
                        <i class="icon text-icon"></i>
                        <span class="txt">我要填写邀请码</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <div class="listItem clearfix">
                        <h3 class="title">邀请码使用说明</h3>
                        <i class="icon down-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                    <ol class="list">
                        <li>积分满90分，才能使用邀请好友功能。</li>
                        <li>注册天数满三天，才能使用验证邀请功能。</li>
                        <li>将您的邀请码分享给好友，对方在注册后，成功验证您的邀请码，双方将各获得100个积分奖励。</li>
                        <li>每个新注册的简拼用户在简拼APP内最多可验证一个邀请码。</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </section>
            <div class="pager-bottom-item"></div>
        </section>
        <!-- 分享弹出层 -->
        <div class="fade"></div>
        <div class="share-pop">
            <div class="list clearfix">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#">
                            <i class="icon weixin-icon"></i>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#">
                            <i class="icon friend-icon"></i>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#">
                            <i class="icon weibo-icon"></i>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="#">
                            <i class="icon qq-icon"></i>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="btn-warp">
                <a href="#" class="btn cancel-btn">取消</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 分享弹出层 end -->
    </body>
</html>